      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">515.3703-1</ph> Acquisition planning.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="id2193F040VYW" class="- topic/p ">Contracting officers shall—<ol class="- topic/ol ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p id="id2193F070P2J" class="- topic/p ">
                     <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> Ensure
plans comply with <xref href="GSAM-HJESIMSP.dita#HJESIMSP"
                           outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                           class="- topic/xref ">507.104</xref>(d); and</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p id="id2193F070WTA" class="- topic/p ">
                     <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> Select
members of the evaluation team, <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">e.g.</i>, members should include
functional areas such as contracting, small business, technical,
logistics, cost/price, legal, program management and end-user organizations,
when appropriate. Evaluation team members should be told of the
requirement to be available during the evaluation process, time
constraints, and oral feedback meeting.</p>
               </li>
            </ol>
         </p>
